Control your lights, switches and much more with TEP Smartlife. Make your life Smarter with our products!
1. Download our “TEP Smartlife” app in app market then register an account (or log in directly if you already have an account);
2. Configure our devices in “TEP Smartlife” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
3. Enable “TEP Smartlife” skill on Alexa app, you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
4. Tell Echo "Alexa, discover my devices". Wait for Echo to say “Search complete”;
5. Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on the switch.
Alexa, turn off the switch.
Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.
Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.
Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.
Alexa, set the bedroom light to green.
